{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "1.720", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Pr\u00e4sidentin! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "1.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "3.320", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "3.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "6.160", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "6.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "7.720", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Vorwurf, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "7.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "8.720", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "lieber Kollege Gehring, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "8.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "13.200", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wir w\u00fcrden die regelm\u00e4\u00dfige Modernisierung des BAf\u00f6G nicht z\u00fcgig genug vorantreiben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "13.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "16.840", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "verf\u00e4ngt beim allerbesten Willen nicht."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "16.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "22.960", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die 25.\u00a0BAf\u00f6G-Novelle hat erst mit Beginn des Wintersemesters\u00a02016/2017 ihre volle Wirkung entfaltet."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "22.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "26.040", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir brauchen also Zahlen f\u00fcr 2017. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "26.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "27.000", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der BAf\u00f6G-Bericht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "27.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "28.440", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der uns nun vorliegt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "28.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "32.840", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "bildet naturgem\u00e4\u00df nur die Daten der Gef\u00f6rderten f\u00fcr das Jahr\u00a02016 ab. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "32.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "33.480", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das hei\u00dft nun, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "33.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "34.760", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "lieber Herr Kollege Gehring, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "34.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "36.720", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass es heute wirklich zu fr\u00fch ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "36.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "41.560", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "an unserer gro\u00dfen BAf\u00f6G-Reform aus dem Jahr\u00a02015 herumzukritisieren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "41.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "45.120", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das m\u00f6chte ich an dieser Stelle einmal deutlich sagen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "45.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "47.400", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der aktuelle BAf\u00f6G-Bericht zeigt im \u00dcbrigen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "47.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "50.880", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass das BAf\u00f6G seine Funktion insgesamt erf\u00fcllt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "50.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "51.400", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenngleich\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "51.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "52.600", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das ist ja unbestreitbar\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "52.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "56.640", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Zahl der BAf\u00f6G-Empf\u00e4nger im Jahr\u00a02016 gesunken ist."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "56.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "58.280", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Was sind die Ursachen hierf\u00fcr? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "58.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "62.760", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es sind steigende Einkommen und eine h\u00f6here Erwerbst\u00e4tigkeitsquote in der Bundesrepublik."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "62.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "65.040", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ist also per se kein schlechtes Zeichen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "65.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "66.480", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass es weniger Studierende gibt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "66.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "69.120", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die auf BAf\u00f6G-Leistungen angewiesen sind, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "69.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "70.280", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Kollegin Gohlke. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "70.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "71.840", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es liegt quasi in der Natur der Sache, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "71.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "78.240", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass eine positive wirtschaftliche Entwicklung in Deutschland auch zu einer geringeren Zahl von Gef\u00f6rderten f\u00fchrt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "78.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "82.120", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ungeachtet dessen haben wir mit dem 25.\u00a0BAf\u00f6G-\u00c4nderungsgesetz daf\u00fcr Sorge getragen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "82.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "86.400", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass der Trend einer sinkenden Zahl von Gef\u00f6rderten jedenfalls abgeschw\u00e4cht wurde. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "86.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "89.400", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das hat der Kollege Gehring auch zugestanden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "89.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "95.120", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dass es in Deutschland\u00a02017 \u00fcberhaupt so viele studierende junge Menschen wie noch nie zuvor in der Geschichte der Bundesrepublik gibt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "95.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "97.800", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "n\u00e4mlich 56\u00a0Prozent des Abiturjahrgangs, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "97.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "104.360", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "h\u00e4ngt ebenfalls nicht zuletzt mit der positiven Entwicklung des BAf\u00f6G zusammen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "104.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "105.920", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Gleichwohl sind wir der \u00dcberzeugung\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "105.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "108.520", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und der BAf\u00f6G-Bericht untermauert dies durchaus\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "108.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "115.480", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass es auch in dieser Wahlperiode nach einer entsprechenden Evaluation einer Weiterentwicklung des Bundesausbildungsf\u00f6rderungsgesetzes bedarf. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "115.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "118.920", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Unser Bekenntnis dazu findet sich bereits in unserem Wahlprogramm, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "118.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "123.040", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sp\u00e4testens aber im Papier zum Abschluss der Sondierungsgespr\u00e4che zwischen Union und SPD. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "123.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "124.160", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deshalb, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "124.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "124.880", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "lieber Kollege Gehring, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "124.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "132.360", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "hat es Ihren Antrag und die Aufforderung zu einem z\u00fcgigen Bekenntnis zu einer solchen Reform nun wirklich nicht gebraucht."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "132.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "135.040", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich nehme diese Debatte heute gerne zum Anlass, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "135.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "137.120", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ihnen noch einmal in Erinnerung zu rufen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "137.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "140.040", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "welche zentrale Verbesserung die letzte BAf\u00f6G-Reform, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "140.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "141.240", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die wir hier beschlossen haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "141.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "141.760", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "gebracht hat. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "141.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "148.120", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir haben mit Beginn des Jahres\u00a02015 die volle Finanzierung der Leistungen nach dem BAf\u00f6G \u00fcbernommen\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "148.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "149.880", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "immerhin rund 3\u00a0Milliarden\u00a0Euro pro Jahr\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "149.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "153.720", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und die L\u00e4nder damit um j\u00e4hrlich fast 1,2\u00a0Milliarden\u00a0Euro entlastet. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "153.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "158.680", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das war neben der deutlichen Leistungsausweitung im BAf\u00f6G der entscheidende Durchbruch, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "158.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "161.640", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "161.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "162.680", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Lieber Kollege Gehring, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "162.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "165.040", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "eines \u00fcberrascht mich daher in Ihrem Antrag schon: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "165.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "166.640", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie beschw\u00f6ren hier die Gefahr, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "166.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "171.200", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass durch die alleinige Zust\u00e4ndigkeit des Bundes das BAf\u00f6G nur noch verwaltet, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "171.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "173.040", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber nicht mehr gestaltet wird."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "173.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "173.800", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Also ich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "173.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "175.120", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "175.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "178.200", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "vermisse das Gezerre zwischen Bund und L\u00e4ndern an dieser Stelle nun wirklich nicht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "178.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "178.880", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und ich bin froh, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "178.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "182.440", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir hier im Bundestag mit der Bundesregierung allein gestalten k\u00f6nnen; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "182.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "185.360", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn wir haben in den letzten Jahren hinl\u00e4nglich bewiesen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "185.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "189.080", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass das Thema BAf\u00f6G-Modernisierung bei uns bestens aufgehoben ist."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "189.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "192.120", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Gerade wir waren es in den letzten Jahren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "192.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "193.960", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die immer weitere BAf\u00f6G-Reformen angetrieben haben."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "193.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "195.320", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es waren doch die L\u00e4nder, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "195.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "196.440", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die immer nur geschrien haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "196.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "199.040", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber selber nicht bereit waren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "199.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "199.800", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Geld zu geben."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "199.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "202.440", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "202.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "203.960", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wir schauen daher lieber in die Zukunft. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "203.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "211.480", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir haben im Koalitionsvertrag in Sachen BAf\u00f6G und auch in puncto Verbesserung der sozialen Lage der Studierenden ambitionierte Ziele formuliert; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "211.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "212.440", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das habe ich bereits angedeutet. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "212.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "217.280", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir haben eine deutliche Verbesserung und einen Ausbau des BAf\u00f6G verabredet. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "217.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "224.400", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir wollen im Zeitraum von 2018 bis 2021 rund 1\u00a0Milliarde\u00a0Euro zus\u00e4tzlich aufwenden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "224.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "225.160", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ziel ist es, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "225.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "239.360", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "insbesondere die f\u00f6rderbed\u00fcrftigen Auszubildenden besser zu erreichen und zum Beispiel durch bessere F\u00f6rderm\u00f6glichkeiten f\u00fcr das Teilzeitstudium oder l\u00e4ngere F\u00f6rderzeiten f\u00fcr Studierende mit Kindern mehr Familienfreundlichkeit zu schaffen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "239.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "244.720", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Damit wollen wir die von Ihnen geforderte Trendumkehr bis 2021 schaffen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "244.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "246.040", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Was wir damit auch erreichen wollen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "246.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "246.840", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "246.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "253.040", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist eine weitere St\u00e4rkung der Stipendienkultur und auch der Begabtenf\u00f6rderung in Deutschland. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "253.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "258.480", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir bekennen uns ausdr\u00fccklich auch zur Schaffung von weiterem studentischem Wohnraum."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "258.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "262.680", 
   "id": "s000086", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Viele dieser Themen finden sich sicherlich auch im vorliegenden Antrag wieder. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "262.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "263.600", 
   "id": "s000087", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Was wir aber ablehnen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "263.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "265.440", 
   "id": "s000088", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "lieber Kollege Gehring, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "265.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "267.560", 
   "id": "s000089", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "liebe Kollegen von den Gr\u00fcnen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "267.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "271.040", 
   "id": "s000090", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist die Forderung nach einer automatischen BAf\u00f6G-Anpassung."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "271.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "276.040", 
   "id": "s000091", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir wollen auch in Zukunft die Bedarfss\u00e4tze in regelm\u00e4\u00dfigen Abst\u00e4nden \u00fcberpr\u00fcfen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "276.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "278.360", 
   "id": "s000092", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und zwar anhand der BAf\u00f6G-Berichte. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "278.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "282.920", 
   "id": "s000093", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Einen Automatismus kann es bei diesem lernenden Gesetz nicht geben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "282.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "286.320", 
   "id": "s000094", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir haben im \u00dcbrigen stets auch strukturelle Anpassungen vorgenommen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "286.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "288.360", 
   "id": "s000095", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "beispielsweise beim Thema Bologna, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "288.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "291.040", 
   "id": "s000096", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "beispielsweise beim Thema Onlineantragstellung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "291.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "297.400", 
   "id": "s000097", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Diese Gestaltungsm\u00f6glichkeiten wollen und sollten wir uns als Gesetzgeber in Zukunft nicht nehmen lassen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "297.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "302.080", 
   "id": "s000098", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Was wir ebenfalls ganz bewusst vermeiden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "302.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "306.920", 
   "id": "s000099", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist die Ausgestaltung des BAf\u00f6G als ein Rundum-sorglos-Paket. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "306.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "308.800", 
   "id": "s000100", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das war es im \u00dcbrigen auch nie. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "308.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "315.720", 
   "id": "s000101", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das BAf\u00f6G ist und bleibt eine an der Bed\u00fcrftigkeit der Sch\u00fcler und Studierenden ausgerichtete Sozialleistung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "315.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "318.920", 
   "id": "s000102", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Unser bew\u00e4hrtes Drei-S\u00e4ulen-Modell der Studienfinanzierung\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "318.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "322.040", 
   "id": "s000103", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "neben BAf\u00f6G auch Studienkredite und Stipendien\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "322.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "325.720", 
   "id": "s000104", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "werden wir auch in dieser Legislaturperiode weiter st\u00e4rken."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "325.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "327.880", 
   "id": "s000105", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dabei bleibt das Deutschlandstipendium\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "327.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "329.240", 
   "id": "s000106", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "auch das sage ich hier ausdr\u00fccklich\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "329.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "331.720", 
   "id": "s000107", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ein wichtiger Bestandteil."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "331.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "333.520", 
   "id": "s000108", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich w\u00fcrde mir w\u00fcnschen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "333.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "336.240", 
   "id": "s000109", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass dieses Instrument endlich von allen Fraktionen hier im Hause, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "336.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "338.320", 
   "id": "s000110", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "also auch von den Gr\u00fcnen und den Linken, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "338.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "340.000", 
   "id": "s000111", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Unterst\u00fctzung erfahren w\u00fcrde, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "340.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "340.960", 
   "id": "s000112", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die es verdient. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "340.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "345.000", 
   "id": "s000113", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn die Linken und die Gr\u00fcnen weniger Energie darauf verwenden w\u00fcrden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "345.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "347.120", 
   "id": "s000114", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das Deutschlandstipendium schlechtzureden,"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "347.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "350.400", 
   "id": "s000115", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
