   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "375.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "378.560", 
   "id": "s000125", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ist die Antragstellung vielleicht doch zu b\u00fcrokratisch? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "378.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "381.480", 
   "id": "s000126", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Will man dem Stigma der Hilfsbed\u00fcrftigkeit entgehen? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "381.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "383.800", 
   "id": "s000127", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ist es vielleicht die Angst vor der Verschuldung? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "383.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "389.320", 
   "id": "s000128", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Verzichten anspruchsberechtigte Studierende ganz bewusst auf BAf\u00f6G-Leistungen und gehen lieber arbeiten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "389.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "392.960", 
   "id": "s000129", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
