   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "392.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "398.520", 
   "id": "s000130", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "All diese Fragen scheinen aus unserer Sicht noch nicht abschlie\u00dfend beantwortet zu sein."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "398.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "403.160", 
   "id": "s000131", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir werden im Gesetzgebungsverfahren dar\u00fcber sicherlich noch ausf\u00fchrlich sprechen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "403.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "405.520", 
   "id": "s000132", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Eine Werbekampagne ist dann eine m\u00f6gliche L\u00f6sung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "405.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "408.920", 
   "id": "s000133", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "meine Damen und Herren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "408.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "410.600", 
   "id": "s000134", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zusammengefasst: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "410.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "415.080", 
   "id": "s000135", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die BAf\u00f6G-Novelle wird nach einer entsprechenden sorgf\u00e4ltigen Evaluation kommen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "415.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "418.360", 
   "id": "s000136", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Einige der von den Gr\u00fcnen genannten Punkte werden sich darin wiederfinden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "418.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "420.080", 
   "id": "s000137", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "andere ganz sicherlich nicht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "420.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "420.880", 
   "id": "s000138", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir machen das, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "420.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "421.280", 
   "id": "s000139", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie gewohnt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "421.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "424.280", 
   "id": "s000140", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in einem ordentlichen parlamentarischen Verfahren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "424.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "428.320", 
   "id": "s000141", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir freuen uns dabei auf die wichtigen Erkenntnisse aus den BAf\u00f6G-Berichten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "428.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "429.920", 
   "id": "s000142", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie alle sind herzlich eingeladen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "429.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "432.400", 
   "id": "s000143", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sich an diesem Diskussionsprozess zu beteiligen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "432.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "433.040", 
   "id": "s000144", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Danke sehr."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "433.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "442.000", 
   "id": "s000145", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zu ihrer ersten Rede im Deutschen Bundestag erteile ich der Abgeordneten Dr.\u00a0Manja Sch\u00fcle aus der SPD-Fraktion das Wort."
   ]
  }
